Editing Contract Details, after clicking on Save an undefined Contract Details details record is returned.



Key details
Description

When editing Contract Details, after clicking on Save an undefined Contract Details details record is returned.

To resolve item 7. Medium priority: When editing Contract Details, after clicking on Save does not refresh immeidately an undefined Contract Details details record is returned. Jira: FOC-54 tested and passed in Blue / / / FOC-567 is in play too not show stopper



Root cause: OC uses contract detail business key to identify which contract in case detail to resolve bug FOC-567. But the business key was changed after user updated contract detail data, and frontend was used old business key to refresh data.


Solution 2: (Good)

OM: Alex Benning Lorean De Vries Provide new API to update contract detail and return new contract business key which use to refresh data in Contract Detail page.

OC: we will implement this API.



Props: It can resolve the cause at root.

Cons: Take more effort.



